resources.string:
Witness Barney Stinson's most awesome moments now. Everywhere. Knowing how much you love Barney Stinson, we collected hundreds of audio recordings of his most awesome moments. A clear and eye-pleasing layout emphasizes this app's quality.

Don't hesitate and test this amazing Android app now:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.troubi.barneystinsonsoundboard
Barney Stinson Soundboard. Only for Android.
All snippets are from the tv-series \"How I Met Your Mother.\"\nThe developers of this app did not create this content.
